A 53-year old man, Umar Maigoro of Pompomari, Damakasu street of Damaturu, Yobe State has been arrested by the Yob Police Command for impregnating his 14-year old biological daughter. The victim who is in JSS 3 is said to be carrying a 4-month old pregnancy allegedly by her biological father. The suspect who had earlier sent the daughter to the village to cover up the shameful act, on interrogation confessed to have slept with the victim several times but denied being responsible for the pregnancy. The randy father, Umar Maigoro who sells kola-nut (Goro) at Damaturu main motor park had divorced the victimâ€™s mother and taken another wife.